<div class="text-block__content text-block__content--image">
<h4 class="text-block__subtitle">
        Our Story
       </h4>
<h2 class="text-block__title">
        Why did we create Startpage.com?
       </h2>
<p class="p1">
<span style="font-weight: 400;">
         As kids, we’re all taught not to touch stuff that doesn’t belong to us. It’s a good guideline. So why are online companies harvesting our personal data without our consent? They shouldn’t. That’s why we’re developing online tools that help you stay in control of your personal information. Search is done. Expect other private versions of common digital services soon. Why?
        </span>
</p>
<p class="p1">
<strong>
         Because it’s our belief that personal data should be your data, not Big Data. Period.
        </strong>
</p>
</div>
<noscript>
<img alt="Shredder" class="text-block__image" src="/assets/images/dtc/1537264762-homepage-why.svg?v=816c5d8d"/>
</noscript>
<img alt="Shredder" class="text-block__image" data-lazy-load="" data-src="/assets/images/dtc/1537264762-homepage-why.svg?v=816c5d8d"/>
</section>
<div class="tech">

<div class="text-block__content">
<h4 class="text-block__subtitle">
         The Tech
        </h4>
<h2 class="text-block__title">
         How we made search private
        </h2>
<p class="p1">
<span style="font-weight: 400;">
          You can’t beat Google when it comes to online search. So we’re paying them to use their brilliant search results in order to remove all trackers and logs. The result: The world’s best and most private search engine. Only now you can search without ads following you around, recommending products you’ve already bought. And no more data mining by companies with dubious intentions. We want you to dance like nobody’s watching
         </span>
<em>
<span style="font-weight: 400;">
           and
          </span>
</em>
<span style="font-weight: 400;">
          search like nobody’s watching.
         </span>
</p>
<a class="button button--primary button--big" data-show-overlay="data-button1" href="/en/search/download-startpage-plugin.html">
         Make Startpage.com your default search engine
        </a>
</div>
</section>

<div class="text-image-block__content clearfix">
<div class="text-image-block__image">
<noscript>
<img alt="" src="/assets/images/dtc/1537265485-homepage-no-data.svg?v=8f6990f5"/>
</noscript>
<img alt="" data-lazy-load="" data-src="/assets/images/dtc/1537265485-homepage-no-data.svg?v=8f6990f5"/>
</div>
<div class="text-image-block__body">
<h2 class="text-image-block__title">
          No personal data storage
         </h2>
<p>
<span style="font-weight: 400;">
           We don’t collect or share your personal information. Ever. There’s literally no data about you on our servers. None. We can’t profile you, and we can’t be forced to hand over your data to authorities, simply because we don’t have any data to hand over.
          </span>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="text-image-block block--white text-image-block--large">
<div class="text-image-block__content clearfix">
<div class="text-image-block__image">
<noscript>
<img alt="Bagman" src="/assets/images/dtc/1537265474-homepage-visit-anonymously.svg?v=4a555738"/>
</noscript>
<img alt="Bagman" data-lazy-load="" data-src="/assets/images/dtc/1537265474-homepage-visit-anonymously.svg?v=4a555738"/>
</div>
<div class="text-image-block__body">
<h2 class="text-image-block__title">
          Anonymous View
         </h2>
<p>
<span style="font-weight: 400;">
           Clicking search results means leaving the protection of Startpage.com. This could lead to a barrage of cookies being installed on your device. That’s why we developed the "Anonymous View" feature. With "Anonymous View" you can visit search results in full privacy, and keep on browsing: They’ll never know you were there. You’ll find the feature next to every search result.
          </span>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="text-image-block block--white text-image-block--align-right text-image-block--large">

</noscript>
<img alt="" data-lazy-load="" data-src="/assets/images/dtc/1537265495-homepage-no-filter.svg?v=6308175d"/>
</div>
<div class="text-image-block__body">
<h2 class="text-image-block__title">
          No filter bubble
         </h2>
<p>
<span style="font-weight: 400;">
           Other search engines use your search habits to serve you results they think you want, essentially trapping you in an echo chamber of results. With Startpage.com, you break through the filter bubble to see a wider variety of results.
          </span>
</p>
